<node CREATED="1286397912370" ID="ID_1944723679" MODIFIED="1286397952242" TEXT="Provide the programming support that allows you to run Selenium commands from a program of your own design. A Selenium client library provides a programming interface (API), i.e., a set of functions, which run Selenium commands from your own program."/>
